land, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with William Richard Woodcock."},"et":{"Abt. 1264–":"umbes 1264–Surnud","1260–1298":"1260–1298","1286–1308":"1286–1308","1264–Female":"1264–Surnud","1298":"1298","1264":"1264","1286":"1286","Abt. 1264":"umbes 1264","Abt. 1286":"umbes 1286","1260":"1260","1308":"1308","of, Walton, Lancashire, England":"Walton on the Hill, Lancashire, England","Walton Le Dale, Lancashire, England":"Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt. 1264–":"noin 1264–Kuollut","1260–1298":"1260–1298","1286–1308":"1286–1308","1264–Female":"1264–Kuollut","1298":"1298","1264":"1264","1286":"1286","Abt. 1264":"noin 1264","Abt. 1286":"noin 1286","1260":"1260","1308":"1308","of, Walton, Lancashire, England":"Walton on the Hill, Lancashire, England","Walton Le Dale, Lancashire, England":"Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt. 1264–":"environ 1264–Décédée","1260–1298":"1260–1298","1286–1308":"1286–1308","1264–Female":"1264–Décédée","1298":"1298","1264":"1264","1286":"1286","Abt. 1264":"environ 1264","Abt. 1286":"environ 1286","1260":"1260","1308":"1308","of, Walton, Lancashire, England":"Walton on the Hill, Lancashire, Angleterre","Walton Le Dale, Lancashire, England":"Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Woodcock est née environ 1264, à Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William Richard Woodcock."},"de":{"Abt. 1264–":"um 1264–Verstorben","1260–1298":"1260–1298","1286–1308":"1286–1308","1264–Female":"1264–Verstorben","1298":"1298","1264":"1264","1286":"1286","Abt. 1264":"um 1264","Abt. 1286":"um 1286","1260":"1260","1308":"1308","of, Walton, Lancashire, England":"Walton on the Hill, Lancashire, England","Walton Le Dale, Lancashire, England":"Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Woodcock wurde um 1264 in Walton-le-Dale, Lancashire, England, United Kingdom geboren. Sie hatte mit William Ri